Class Format

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.media.common.Format

      • getFormatArrays

        public Format.FormatArrays getFormatArrays​()
        Creates a FormatArrays instance with formatMap key-value pairs.

        formatMap key-value pairs are in the (key1, value1), ..., (keyN, valueN) format, and the created FormatArrays instance has the following structure:

        keys: key1,key2, ... , keyN

        values: value1, value2, ... , valueN

        Notice this function would also convert byte[] value to a ByteBuffer value.

        Returns:
        Returns a FormatArrays instance.
        Since:
        1
